Follow these steps to get DRAMSim3 as part of gem5

1. Download DRAMSim3
```
sudo apt install cmake
```
```
cd  GEM5/ext/dramsim3 # this directory
```
```
set -e
git clone https://github.com/umd-memsys/DRAMsim3.git DRAMsim3
cd DRAMsim3 && mkdir build -p
cd build
cmake ..
make
cd ../../../../
```

2. Compile gem5
    2.1 cd gem5
    2.2 Business as usual

